data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent1
data.value: Potential customers turn to Plansy to find the service they need in their city. You reach new customers without any costs for you.

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent2
data.value: Due to the clever agenda, customers book appointments directly into your agenda on a time convenient for them and for you. New appointments are made, even at times your business is closed. Instead of being on the telephone you can focus on your business.

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent3
data.value: Plansy is synced with your own agenda. You keep all your appointments conveniently in one place.

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent4
data.value: The automated reminders reduce no shows. Customers receive a reminder on their phone and will not forget their appointments.

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent5
data.value: There are no monthly service fees. You only pay for results. Only after appointments have been made you pay a small fee. We only charge €25,- just once to set up your profile. Sign up and try it now.

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent6
data.value: In Plansy, you have all your customers in one place, and you can easily sent individual or group messages or ads for your business. Plansy takes care of the rest, sending notification messages to everyone!

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent7
data.value: Customers schedule appointments with your business on the go, at work or at home. Plansy is optimized for mobile devices with apps for iPhone, iPad and Android smartphones. Customers can reach your business anywhere, anytime.

data.name: LandingPageNew_BoxContent8
data.value: Block times and days, so customers can only schedule appointments on times that are convenient for you. You receive a notification when appointments are scheduled. After your approval the customers receives a confirmation of the appointment.
